# Contribution & Measurement Guidelines

This directory defines the operational rules for maintaining theoretical integrity within the IPP repository.

## Files
- **version_control.md** — Rules for modifying core models and architectural layers.
- **measurement_mismatch.md** — Schema for documenting the orthogonal complement (X⊥) when proposing new metrics.

These guidelines ensure that all contributions remain aligned with L0/L1 material constraints and avoid administrative distortion.
